@NODE "Introduction" "Introduction"
@{b}Introduction:@{ub}

Let the Sysop have FAVORITE file(s) that users can download
from any prompt. (Personaly I had a picture of my girlfrend :-)

@ENDNODE

@NODE "Installation" "Installation"
@{b}Installation:@{ub}

Copy all files in archive to PFiles.
GiveUser command in Sys:C (Not included)

Edit the file SysopFavorite.Rexx and config after your needs.
Also edit the *.ANSI files if want...

Input this line under menu 2; Available everywhere in your BBSMenu:
FAVOrite        `0-|#0PFiles:SysopFavorite/SysopFavorite.Rexx}
@ENDNODE

@NODE "Requirements" "Requirements"
@{b}Requirements:@{ub}

